title: Sunset of Tomorrow
info:
explizit     
is proud              
         to           
         present:     
                      
 sunset of tomorrow   
                      
                      
written by KoM'AH     
                      
finished on 17-08-96  
                      
- PLAY IN FT2.06 !!! -
songlength: 9:05

   style: drum 'n bass
                      
well here's the song  
i told you about in my
previous production.  
it's a long track,yes,
again, but that's a   
normal phenomenon     
in the drum 'n bass   
scene... so all you   
3minute-shortsong-    
raveonly-lowlife shut 
up, or delete this xm 
right away, you can't 
make me move. ha!     
greetinx to all scene 
geezers around the    
world worth greeting, 
and to all my personal
friends..... who will 
probably only get to  
hear this on tape,    
'cos they don't have  
the proper stuph for  
these musicphilez ;)  
                      
of course special     
greetz 'n respect to  
all drum 'n bass fans 
around the globe..    
( i guess most of 'em 
 are english ;) )     
and i hope one of     
the following guys    
gets to hear this:    
                      
LTJ Bukem / PFM       
Peshay / Goldie       
Future Bound / Skanna 
Aphrodite /  Photek   
M-Beat / Alex Reece,  
keep up the very very 
good work! you're     
music elevates our    
minds 'n stuph...     
at least it's very    
relaxing music you    
bring forth....       
                      
but 'nuff said... i'm 
wasting time typing   
crap here and i don't 
WANT to fill up this  
space like some of    
you porkfaces do...so 
i say.. bye!
